  "title": "Logistics, Business Support Team Lead",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>GeneralSummary:</strong></u></p><p><br />The Business support team in the following areas: transportation mode strategy, operational and business unit support. This position has fundamental responsibility to drive continuous improvement in transportation and services. </p><p>This role plays an important part in ensuring that our fulfillment goals are consistently met on a daily basis.</p><p><u><strong>Essentialduties and Responsibilities: </strong></u></p><p><strong>Essential Duties & Responsibilities </strong></p><p>Responsible for issuing delivery document and collaborate with transportation service provider. </p><p>Responsible for customer servicing purchase order.</p><p>Responsible for the overall key metrics for the specific transportation mode including On-Time Arrival, Variable Distribution, and </p><p>Customer Complaints as related to Logistics.</p><p>Analyze data related to key metrics to identify trends and root causes to developcorrective action and drive continuous improvement.</p><p>Own and maintain all SOP and training documentation.</p><p>Support batch management & stock requisition request & comply FIFO.</p><p>Support warehouse operation.<br /></p><p>Please take note: 3 months contract and may extend </p>",
